original_title: Rod Z: I Ain't Lied Yet!
overview: Comedy, Stand-Up - Laughter is often the best medicine for what ails you. With a desire to touch lives through the healing balm of humor, jokester Rod Z has created another comedic gem. In his sophomore release -- "I Ain't Lied Yet!" -- this funnyman of The Most High shines with energy and hilarious on-target stories that connect with and captivate his audience. Get ready for an amusing yet refreshing outlook on life; it's a real bull's eye.
title: Rod Z: I Ain't Lied Yet!
